Jingle All the Way;;38;;20;;PG;;Workaholic Howard Langston (Arnold Schwarzenegger) wants to make things up to his son, Jamie (Jake Lloyd), and wife, Liz (Rita Wilson). He promises to get Jamie the hottest toy of the season, Turbo-Man -- even though it's Christmas Eve and the toy is practically sold out. As Langston hunts down the elusive gift, he runs into mailman Myron (Sinbad), another father on the same quest. With the clock winding down, Langston's moral code is tested as he starts to learn the real meaning of Christmas.;;Comedy,Kids & family,Other;;Brian Levant;;1996;;Arnold Schwarzenegger,Sinbad,Phil Hartman,Rita Wilson,Robert Conrad,Martin Mull,Jake Lloyd,Jim Belushi,Harvey Korman,Laraine Newman;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/jingle_all_the_way